{"tid":1488842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"超緊急!! 用Twitter文宣既大家快d入","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T23:45:07.000Z","uid":184581,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d4cd92be94964137ee7fb3c4dd466021e045ae","tid":1488842,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"大家唔好只係用轉推文既方式做文宣<br />\n呢一種做法對真正用Twitter既用家做成好<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大影響</span></strong></span>(好似比人洗版咁)<br />\n好似呢個人咁 我見佢加左追隨左好多香港做文宣既朋友<br />\n佢講要大家停止呢一種亂TAG 同大量既轉推文既行為 做成一種好討厭既感覺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rpgxeAh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrpgxeAh.png&h=7cd4e2e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.請大家最多TAG 3 - 4個就夠 唔好亂TAG<br />\n2.見到差唔多既文就唔好再轉推 會令FOLLOW左你既人好困擾<br />\n3.多D用回覆同like下人<br />\n4.Follow 戰友"},{"pid":"3231799ba2ecafcf9a5dc5c1a815d410a64bc621","tid":1488842,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:06:34.000Z","msg":"推我呀"},{"pid":"ee05cde39169c9dde90aff08313d85550ea03de9","tid":1488842,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:06:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>Fight for freedom<br />\nStand with Hong Kong</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n821/823/831 死線（未定好）<br />\n<br />\n823人鏈<br />\n<br />\n824 去完觀塘再入機場<br />\n<br />\n825 荃葵青<br />\n<br />\n831 中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n9月三罷<br />\n<br />\n不分和勇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"68fb7000bc8a767316d88e79e4cde1a2cfde1015","tid":1488842,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:07:06.000Z","msg":"（整合） 